author: By DAVID KLEPPER, BEATRICE DUPUY and MEG KINNARD Associated Press
title: In pandemic, rumors of martial law fly despite reassurances
description: NEW YORK (AP) — Millions of Americans have been ordered to stay home. Businesses and schools are shuttered. And National Guard units have been activated in more than half the states.
